001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 55,
011    displayName = "Bolus Activated",
012    internalName = "LID_BOLUS_ACTIVATED",
013    usedByTidepool = true
014)
015public class BolusActivatedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
016    
017    private int bolusId;
018    private float iob;
019    private float bolusSize;
020    
021    public BolusActivatedHistoryLog() {}
022    public BolusActivatedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, float iob, float bolusSize) {
023        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
024        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, bolusId, iob, bolusSize);
025        this.bolusId = bolusId;
026        this.iob = iob;
027        this.bolusSize = bolusSize;
028        
029    }
030
031    public BolusActivatedHistoryLog(int bolusId, float iob, float bolusSize) {
032        this(0, 0, bolusId, iob, bolusSize);
033    }
034
035    public int typeId() {
036        return 55;
037    }
038
039    /**
040     * <table border="1">
041     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolusActivatedHistoryLog:</caption>
042     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>iob</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>bolusSize</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
045     * </table>
046     */
047    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
048        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
049        this.cargo = raw;
050        parseBase(raw);
051        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
052        this.iob = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
053        this.bolusSize = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
054        
055    }
056
057    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, float iob, float bolusSize) {
058        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
059            new byte[]{55, 0},
060            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
061            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
062            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
063            Bytes.toFloat(iob), 
064            Bytes.toFloat(bolusSize)));
065    }
066    public int getBolusId() {
067        return bolusId;
068    }
069    public float getIob() {
070        return iob;
071    }
072    public float getBolusSize() {
073        return bolusSize;
074    }
075    
076}
